org.apache.hadoop.fs.swift.http

类 SwiftProtocolConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.fs.swift.http.SwiftProtocolConstants

  • public class SwiftProtocolConstants
extends Object
    Constants used in the Swift REST protocol, and in the properties used to configure the SwiftRestClient.
